Class JsonSerializable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.cosmosdb.JsonSerializable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConsistencyPolicy, DatabaseAccountLocation, ExcludedPath, IncludedPath, Index, IndexingPolicy, PartitionKeyDefinition, ReplicationPolicy, Resource, SqlParameter, SqlQuerySpec, Undefined

    public class JsonSerializable
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a base resource that can be serialized to JSON in the Azure Cosmos DB database service.
